对于 #ce("CHCl2CH2Br(C2H3Cl2Br)")，其同位素峰组为：

$
  (100_M + 0.016_(M+1))^3 (100_M + 1.08_(M+1))^2 (100_M + 32.5_(M+2))^2 (100_M + 98.0_(M+2))^1
$

其中：

$
  (100_M + 0.016_(M+1))^3
  &= 100^3_M + 3 times 100^2 times 0.016_(M+1) + 3 times 100 times 0.016^2_(M+2) + 0.016^3_(M+3) \
  &= 10^6_M + 480_(M+1) + 0.0768_(M+2) + 4.096 times 10^(-6)_(M+3) \
  (100_M + 1.08_(M+1))^2
  &= 100^2_M + 2 times 100 times 1.08_(M+1) + 1.08^2_(M+2) \
  &= 10^4_M + 216_(M+2) + 1.166_(M+2) \
  (100_M + 32.5_(M+2))^2
  &= 100^2_M + 2 times 100 times 32.5_(M+2) + 32.5^2_(M+4) \
  &= 10^4_M + 6.5 times 10^3_(M+2) + 1.056 times 10^3_(M+4) \
  (100_M + 98.0_(M+2))^1
  &= 100_M + 98.0_(M+2)
$

即 $(1)$ 式展开得：

$
  10^16_M + 2.208 times 10^14_(M+1) + 1.631 times 10^16_(M+2) + 3.568 times 10^14_(M+3) \
  + 7.427 times 10^15_(M+4) + 1.640 times 10^14_(M+5) + 1.036 times 10^15_(M+6) + 2.285 times 10^13_(M+7) \
  + 1.316 times 10^11_(M+8) + 5.964 times 10^7_(M+9) + 9.311 times 10^3_(M+10) + 0.494_(M+11)
$

从而：

$
  M : M+1 : M+2 : M+3 : M+4 : M+5 : M+6 : M+7 : M+8 : M+9 : M+10 : M+11 \
  = 10^16 : 2.208 times 10^14 : 1.631 times 10^16 : 3.568 times 10^14 : 7.427 times 10^15 : 1.640 times 10^14 : \
  1.036 times 10^15 : 2.285 times 10^13 : 1.316 times 10^11 : 5.964 times 10^7 : 9.311 times 10^3 : 0.494
$

